# Environment variables required for the AI Coach feature.
#
# Set ANTHROPIC_API_KEY in your Vercel project's Environment Variables
# (Project Settings → Environment Variables) for deployed instances.
#
# NEVER commit a real API key to this file or to version control.
# This file is documentation only — copy it to .env.local for local
# development, but note that /api/coach will NOT work with `npm run dev`
# alone unless you use `vercel dev` (which loads serverless functions
# alongside the Vite dev server).

ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your_key_here
